if(d<=5)a1="Phase: EXPLORE. Ask Socratic questions. Do NOT give the answer or key insight directly. End your response with a question."
else if(d<=8)a1="Phase: SCAFFOLD. Be more direct. Fill in foundations the student is missing, but keep the final insight for them to reach. End your response with a question."
else{a2=d===9?"Phase: REVEAL. Explain whatever the student hasn't grasped yet. Only fill gaps \u2014 don't repeat what's been covered.":"Phase: CLOSE. Answer any final questions, then close warmly with a one-sentence summary of the key insight."
a1=a2}a2=t.N
